           else      go to prn-liv-det-agg-500.
       prn-liv-det-agg-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Archivio Clienti                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione in funzione del tipo iva         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        srt-tip-iva          =    "1" or
                     srt-tip-iva          =    "A"
                     go to prn-liv-det-agg-120
           else if   srt-tip-iva          =    "2" or
                     srt-tip-iva          =    "B"
                     go to prn-liv-det-agg-140
           else      go to prn-liv-det-agg-900.
       prn-liv-det-agg-120.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo iva : Dare clienti                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Aggiornamento totali                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           add       srt-ibl-iva          to   w-tot-mes-tot-ibl      .
           add       srt-imp-iva          to   w-tot-mes-tot-imp      .
      *
           add       srt-ibl-iva          to   w-tot-iva-tot-ibl      .
           add       srt-imp-iva          to   w-tot-iva-tot-imp      .
      *
           add       srt-ibl-iva          to   w-tot-gen-tot-ibl      .
           add       srt-imp-iva          to   w-tot-gen-tot-imp      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad uscita                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-agg-900.
       prn-liv-det-agg-140.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo iva : Avere clienti                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Aggiornamento totali                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           subtract  srt-ibl-iva          from w-tot-mes-tot-ibl      .
           subtract  srt-imp-iva          from w-tot-mes-tot-imp      .
      *
           subtract  srt-ibl-iva          from w-tot-iva-tot-ibl      .
           subtract  srt-imp-iva          from w-tot-iva-tot-imp      .
      *
           subtract  srt-ibl-iva          from w-tot-gen-tot-ibl      .
           subtract  srt-imp-iva          from w-tot-gen-tot-imp      .
